<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="answer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-container">
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="logo">
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="product.html">Product</a></li>
                <li><a href="">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="answer-card">
            <div class="answer-top">
                <div class="answer-heading heading">
                    <h1>Your sleep quality is:</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <div class="answer-answer-container">
                        <p><%= Math.trunc(sleepQuality) %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feedback-cards">
                <div class="feedback-card feedback-card-1">
                    <div class="feedback-card-top">
                        <h2>Poor</h2>
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-heading heading">
                        <h2>(0 to 3)</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-text">
                        <p>Here are some suggestions to improve sleep:</p>
                        <ul class="suggestions-list">
                            <li>Establish a regular sleep schedule</li>
                            <li>Create a relaxing bedtime routine</li>
                            <li>Make your sleeping environment comfortable</li>
                            <li>Avoid screen time before bed</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feedback-card feedback-card-2">
                    <div class="feedback-card-top">
                        <h2>Moderate</h2>
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-heading heading">
                        <h2>(4 to 7)</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-text">
                        <p>Here are some suggestions to improve sleep:</p>
                        <ul class="suggestions-list">
                            <li>Continue with your sleep schedule</li>
                            <li>Limit caffeine and alcohol intake</li>
                            <li>Practice relaxation techniques before bedtime</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feedback-card feedback-card-3">
                    <div class="feedback-card-top">
                        <h2>Excellent</h2>
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-heading heading">
                        <h2>(7 to 10)</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-card-text">
                        <p>Here are some suggestions to improve sleep:</p>
                        <ul class="suggestions-list">
                            <li>Keep a consistent sleep schedule</li>
                            <li>Engage in regular physical activity</li>
                            <li>Create a peaceful and comfortable sleep environment</li>
                            <li>Avoid heavy meals before bedtime</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</body>
</html>